Package: ip2location.io
Title: Batch IP Data Retrieval and Storage Using 'IP2Location.io'
Version: 0.0.0-2
Authors@R: 
    person("Oriane", "Georgeac", email = "oriane.georgeac@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6531-0075"))
Description: A system for submitting multiple IP information queries to 'IP2Location.io'â€™s IP Geolocation API and storing the resulting data in a dataframe. You provide a vector of IP addresses and your 'IP2Location.io' API key. The package returns a dataframe with one row per IP address and a column for each available data field (data fields not included in your API plan will contain NAs). This is the second submission of the package to CRAN.
